\fs28 \cf0 4.1 Invoice Rules to Enforce\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs26 \cf0 \uc0\u9989 
\f4  REQUIRED VALIDATIONS:\
- Invoice number must be unique per business\
- Invoice date cannot be in the future (for sent invoices)\
- Due date must be >= invoice date\
- At least one line item required\
- Total must be > 0\
- Client must be selected\
\

\f2 \uc0\u10060 
\f4  DO NOT ENFORCE:\
- Specific invoice number formats (let users customize)\
- Tax ID format validation (too many edge cases)\
- Currency restrictions (users know their clients)\
- Maximum line items (no arbitrary limits)\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

